{
  "text": "A series of 200 observations are given by equations in (1) and the initial conditions are given as follows: [CITATION_1] Under the same conditions, simulations are done by using three algorithms, namely, SIS/resampling algorithm, resample-move algorithm, and our algorithm. For the purpose of comparison, we plot the simulation results of three algorithm into one figure.",
  "correct_citation": {
